The results suggest that the corporation should launch the mine. Positive net present value ($1,564,600,000) is achieved within a reasonable timeframe of 4 years; internal rate of return (IRR) and modified internal rate of return (MIRR) both exceed the minimum needed return rate (ROR) of 12%. However, before making a call, it's vital to take into account things like the market, the competitors, and any relevant regulations. 